snippet.title: Crash Bash LIVE - The Holiday Special
snippet.description:
A special holiday message from the Viscount to all viewers of Crash Bash LIVE!

Holiday cosmetics now available annually from December until the end of February!

This build is now available for testing ONLY on https://crashbash.live/
(The ONLY official page of the project. We are not responsible for any damages caused by using any other sources.)

Credits:

TEAM NITRO
 Aaron Pieries (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCi2SGWCzyyIeC8-03eqOPMA) - Voice Acting
 Ashy666 (https://ashy666.deviantart.com/) - Texturing
 BetaM (https://www.youtube.com/mat5b) - Lead developer, Programmer, Designer
 Keon McKeon (https://www.youtube.com/user/theb13maker) - Voice Acting
 Lurking Leanne (http://lurking-leanne.deviantart.com/) - Art, Texturing
 Mewsel (https://www.youtube.com/user/Mewsel/videos) - Voice Acting (Planned)
 Mike Gomez (https://www.artstation.com/artist/theredwall66) - 3D Art
 PolyG (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw_HjqMDz7A0thJow6seSuA) - Modelling, Texturing, Animating, SFX
 Smaz (https://www.youtube.com/user/SmazUgonih) - Writing (Planned)
 Syphyous Gestmorph (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_ml46Nn3yjpHe5bt073MYg) - Voice Acting (The Viscount)
 XenoMind (http://xenomind.deviantart.com/) - Modelling, Texturing

SPECIAL THANKS
 BandicootUnit (https://facepunch.com/member.php?u=648498) - Temporary boss model (Papu)
 Bror (http://www.twitch.tv/brormanis) - Guest Voice Acting, Internal Testing
 CRASHARKI (http://crasharki.deviantart.com/) - Mask models, Temporary Nina model
 DemonBoy (http://o0demonboy0o.deviantart.com/) - Art assistance
 FireWavezZ (https://www.youtube.com/user/llCalicoJackll) - Crate textures
 MikeyM92 (http://mikeym92.deviantart.com/) - Logo
 Natty (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWXsvUMyOf_OpfdrFoyRZYA) - Internal Testing
 PeteThePlayer (https://www.youtube.com/user/PeteThePlayer) - Guest Voice Acting
 Pull (http://www.twitch.tv/pwulla) - Internal Testing
 Staniel (http://www.youtube.com/DTW1996) - Temporary boss model (Oxide)
